Package: rust-spooler
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, cups, cups-client
Description: FLUX ERP to CUPS Print Server Bridge
 A Rust-based print spooler that bridges between FLUX ERP and local CUPS
 printers. Features include:
 .
 - Real-time WebSocket integration with Laravel Reverb
 - Automatic printer discovery and synchronization
 - Multi-instance support with configurable filtering
 - TUI-based configuration interface
 - Support for both polling and WebSocket modes